      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 06:46:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>就业配额抗议活动蔓延 孟加拉国面临停摆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-faces-nationwide-shutdown-as-jobs-protest-escalates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在示威活动演变为暴力事件后，学生抗议者向总理谢赫·哈西娜施压，要求废除政府的就业配额制度，孟加拉国将从周四开始关闭交通网络和企业。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/bangladesh-faces-nationwide-shutdown-as-jobs-protest-escalates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 05:14:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙临时政府已准备好长期执政法国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/macron-s-caretaker-government-is-digging-in-for-the-long-haul</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙正在为在未来数月内以权力有限的看守政府来管理法国做准备，因为他将把法国推向未知的宪法领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-18/macron-s-caretaker-government-is-digging-in-for-the-long-haul</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Jul 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
